In the INTEREST OF C.H. and D.H., Minor Children, W.H., Father, Appellant, C.H., Mother, Appellant. No. 18-1828 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 23, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A mother and father separately appeal a permanency order involving their two children. AFFIRMED IN PART AND REVERSED IN PART ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED IN PART. REVERSED IN PART ON BOTH APPEALS.
